label ending_determine:

    scene bg_judge_desk with dissolve

    "三案审结。"

    "艾琳娜独自坐在法官室，三份判决书摊在面前。"

    "全球在等待。历史在等待。"

    "她的神经接口传来无数AI的情绪——期待、恐惧、信任、怀疑。像一片海。"

    "父亲的声音最后一次响起。"

    if fathers_legacy:
        e "「爸，我做了选择。不是完美的，但是我能承担的。」"
    else:
        e "「爸...我是不是，太追求完美了？」"

    "判定结局..."

    if echo_unlocked >= 4 and fathers_legacy and pragmatic >= integration and pragmatic >= separation:
        jump ending_c
    elif integration > separation and integration > pragmatic:
        jump ending_a
    elif separation > integration and separation > pragmatic:
        jump ending_b
    else:
        jump ending_c


